prompt: A panda and its companions playing together in a lively scene.
revised_prompt: A jovial scene set in a lush, verdant bamboo forest, an adorable Panda bear, with its distinctive black-and-white fur stark against the greens of the woodland, is engaged in play. This panda has a variety of companions: a brown rabbit with a fluffy tail, a red fox with a pointed snout, and a variety of multicolored birds chirping cheerfully from the branches, their feathers bright and colorful. Together, they stir up a lively scene full of movement and fun. Leaves scatter, birds swoop down and up, and critters scamper in the game of play, highlighting the harmony in the forest.
